Offer a Smooth Loan Application Review Experience
Make loan decisioning easier for your underwriters by offering them a comprehensive view of the applicant, application, and application form product details.
Give your underwriters access to information about the documents collected and integrations run at various stages of the loan application process.
Empower underwriters to create, track, and review any deviations before they accept a loan application.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Digital Lending—India is enabled.

When: Digital Lending—India is available starting on July 16, 2024.
title: Streamlining Loan Application Review for Underwriters
